          </mxGeometry>
        </mxCell>
        <mxCell id="KddbgMC1e0UQ3pf7TUQQ-8" value="&lt;h1 style=&quot;margin-top: 0px;&quot;&gt;Key Features&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style=&quot;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;&lt;br/&gt; margin-bottom:0in&quot; type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt; &lt;li style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt&quot;&gt;Sealed Class:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt&quot;&gt; Prevents&lt;br&gt;     subclassing, which could otherwise violate the singleton pattern.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt; &lt;li style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt&quot;&gt;Private Constructor:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;     Ensures no other part of the code can execute new Logger().&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt; &lt;li style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt&quot;&gt;Lazy&amp;lt;Logger&amp;gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt&quot;&gt; * &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt&quot;&gt;Lazy&lt;br&gt;     Initialization:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;     The logger/singleton isn&#39;t created until the exact moment Logger.Instance is called&lt;br&gt;     for the first time. If your app never logs anything, it never wastes&lt;br&gt;     memory.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt; &lt;ul style=&quot;direction:ltr;unicode-bidi:embed;margin-top:0in;&lt;br/&gt;  margin-bottom:0in&quot; type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;  &lt;li style=&quot;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:0;vertical-align:middle&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight:bold;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt&quot;&gt;Thread&lt;br&gt;      Safety:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Calibri;font-size:11.0pt&quot;&gt; If&lt;br&gt;      multiple threads try to access Logger.Instance at the exact same&lt;br&gt;      millisecond, Lazy&amp;lt;T&amp;gt; guarantees that only one instance is created&lt;br&gt;      safely without complex lock blocks.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;br&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;" style="text;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;overflow=hidden;rounded=0;" vertex="1" parent="1">
          <mxGeometry x="40" y="270" width="550" height="440" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
